    <stitle>FRONT DRIVE AXLE WHEEL ENDS: FABCO SDA-12 - LUBRICATION - TIE ROD ENDS</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="lubricate" graphiccount="0">
        <title>TIE ROD ENDS</title>
        <para>Tie rod ends should be lubricated every 1,000 miles with chassis lubricant (
            <hotlnk document="s02010_41.xml" xrefid="f0201046">Figure 46</hotlnk>). Check the steering system at each
            lubrication. Inspect for loose, bent or otherwise damaged components. Careful attention to such details is a
            vital safety factor.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
